-hostage-deal-collapsed-after-egypt-secretly-altered-agreement/0000018f-9ed8-da3b-a7ff-9fdd011f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于他的极右翼联盟伙伴，内塔尼亚胡不会抓住美国与沙特的生命线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wont-grab-the-u-s-saudi-lifeline-because-of-his-far-right-coalition-partners/0000018f-9cc2-d35f-a1df-dfcb34ce0000</link><description>尽管美国关于以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间关系正常化的提议充满漏洞，但与利雅得达成的历史性协议可能是他唯一一张“免出狱”牌</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wont-grab-the-u-s-saudi-lifeline-because-of-his-far-right-coalition-partners/0000018f-9cc2-d35f-a1df-dfcb34ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长：国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、加兰特发出逮捕令的请求“毫无根据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-not-planning-to-resettle-gaza-hamas-ouster-essential-for-day-after/0000018f-9df8-d376-a5bf-9ff9990d0000</link><description>报告：美国情报显示三分之一的哈马斯战士被杀，65%的加沙隧道仍然完好 ■ 以色列预备役军人在加沙地带北部与恐怖分子的冲突中受重伤 ■ 美国指责埃及推迟对加沙的人道主义援助 ■ 内塔尼亚胡否认以色列计划重新安置加沙，称哈马斯下台对于“后天”至关重要 ■ 布林肯：由于巴勒斯坦建国，以色列不愿与沙特实现关系正常化</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 01:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israel-not-planning-to-resettle-gaza-hamas-ouster-essential-for-day-after/0000018f-9df8-d376-a5bf-9ff9990d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长为内塔尼亚胡欺诈案辩护作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-testifies-in-support-of-netanyahus-defense-in-yedioth-fraud/0000018f-9ce2-d376-a5bf-9efba4390000</link><description>时任以色列议会内务委员会主席的亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 否认曾于 2014 年会见总理讨论推进以色列哈约姆法 (Yariv Levin)</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 22:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-testifies-in-support-of-netanyahus-defense-in-yedioth-fraud/0000018f-9ce2-d376-a5bf-9efba4390000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员担心以色列对巴勒斯坦国的抵制可能会阻碍沙特实现正常化的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-fear-israeli-pushback-on-palestinian-state-may-hinder-saudi-normalization/0000018f-9d11-d264-a1bf-df9705960000</link><description>美国高级外交官安东尼·布林肯在参议院外交关系委员会作证时概述了华盛顿在促成耶路撒冷和利雅得达成协议方面面临的主要障碍</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 21:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-fear-israeli-pushback-on-palestinian-state-may-hinder-saudi-normalization/0000018f-9d11-d264-a1bf-df9705960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列副市长贴出与蒙眼戴镣铐巴勒斯坦囚犯的嘲讽照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-deputy-mayor-posts-photos-with-blindfolded-shackled-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-9c15-d6da-a1cf-ff379d6b0000</link><description>贝尔谢巴的副市长在加沙战争期间担任约旦河西岸的预备役军人，并在社交媒体上上传了蒙着眼睛的巴勒斯坦人的帖子，并附有嘲讽的标题——军方称这“不符合以色列国防军的价值观”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 20:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-deputy-mayor-posts-photos-with-blindfolded-shackled-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-9c15-d6da-a1cf-ff379d6b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于供应短缺和以色列袭击造成的不安全局势，联合国停止在拉法分发粮食</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</link><description>联合国表示，加沙约有 110 万人（近一半人口）面临灾难性的饥饿，该地区正处于饥荒的边缘。自5月6日以色列入侵拉法以来，人道主义物资危机在两周内加剧</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/un-halts-food-distribution-in-rafah-due-to-supply-shortages-insecurity-from-idf-strikes/0000018f-9c9a-da3b-a7ff-9f9fb1f60000</guid></item><item><title>“让战争机器挨饿”：加州大学圣克鲁斯分校的工人罢工声援亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</link><description>周一，数百名罢工工人在加州大学学校集会，重点关注该州加沙营地的“警察镇压”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/workers-at-uc-santa-cruz-go-on-strike-in-solidarity-with-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-9bf8-da35-a3af-dffa0a620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡已经彻底迷失方向了吗？或许。但也许是故意的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</link><description>人们很容易说，以色列是由一个在严重的政治胁迫下绝望的人领导的，他似乎患有相互交织的综合症，这些综合症曾困扰着他之前的路易十四和沙贝泰·兹维等人。好吧，如果它真的被领导的话</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 18:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/has-netanyahu-completely-lost-his-bearings-maybe-but-maybe-its-intentional/0000018f-9bb6-da35-a3af-dfbeacb70000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷，而不是海牙：以色列必须调查内塔尼亚胡在加沙犯下的危害人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</link><description>回应国际刑事法院逮捕令请求的唯一有效方法是召集以色列国家调查委员会，调查加沙人民是否被故意挨饿——而不是大喊反犹太主义和纳粹主义</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-not-the-hague-israel-must-investigate-netanyahu-for-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-9bee-d6da-a1cf-fbeeec0d0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 228 天：本-格维尔表示，以色列应该在战后控制加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</link><description>以色列敦促“文明世界国家”反对国际刑事法院检察官的要求 ■ 国家安全顾问表示，美国即将与沙特阿拉伯达成升级关系的历史性协议 ■ 本-格维尔：以色列应该在战后控制加沙 ■ 以色列官员夺取广播以色列南部属于美联社的设备 ■ 以色列国防军称其在杰宁发起了反恐行动 ■ 战争进入 228 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-228-israel-should-control-gaza-after-the-war-ben-gvir-says/0000018f-9bfc-d264-a1bf-dfffe0c20000</guid></item><item><title>猛烈抨击国际刑事法院，以色列“官方”反对派像内塔尼亚胡一样懦弱腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</link><description>包括反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德在内的绝大多数以色列议员在一封谴责国际刑事法院检察官汗预审令的信上署名。以色列议会中只有少数人明白，内塔尼亚胡是否“和辛瓦尔一样糟糕”，或者反之亦然，都无关紧要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-21/ty-article/.highlight/slamming-icc-israels-official-opposition-is-as-craven-as-netanyahu-is-corrupt/0000018f-9bde-da35-a3af-dffe8eea0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡警告国际刑事法院的汗：我不担心出国，“他应该担心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡驳回了国际刑事法院针对他和国防部长加兰特的逮捕令申请，称其为“热门工作”，并将其与 9 月 11 日后对乔治·布什或二战后对富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福发出逮捕令进行比较</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-warns-iccs-khan-im-not-concerned-over-going-abroad-he-should-be-worried/0000018f-9b5e-dce9-a1cf-ffde9c400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家档案馆丢失了也门儿童失踪事件的文件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-lose-documents-on-missing-yemenite-children-affair/0000018f-9ae3-da35-a3af-dfeb52a60000</link><description>根据州审计长的报告，一台装有这些文件的电脑被借给了一名员工，但此后就失踪了。报告还发现，138份文件被借给员工且从未归还，并且由于不当行为，信息并未向公众提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-lose-documents-on-missing-yemenite-children-affair/0000018f-9ae3-da35-a3af-dfeb52a60000</guid></item><item><title>阿鲁夫·本：“以色列有办法对抗美国并逃脱惩罚”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-21/ty-article-podcast/aluf-benn-israel-has-a-way-of-standing-up-to-the-u-s-and-getting-away-with-it/0000018f-9b0f-dce9-a1cf-ffcf7f2d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-21/ty-article-podcast/aluf-benn-israel-has-a-way-of-standing-up-to-the-u-s-and-getting-away-with-it/0000018f-9b0f-dce9-a1cf-ffcf7f2d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列驻瑞典大使在持续威胁下保持乐观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ambassador-to-sweden-remains-optimistic-while-working-under-constant-threats/0000018f-9a6c-dce9-a1cf-feecb91f0000</link><description>齐夫·内沃·库尔曼 (Ziv Nevo Kulman) 于 2021 年上任，当时正值以色列-瑞典关系史上最困难的危机之一。 10 月 7 日，其他声音也浮出水面。他在接受《国土报》采访时表示，“突然间，我们发现在核心问题上达成了共识”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ambassador-to-sweden-remains-optimistic-while-working-under-constant-threats/0000018f-9a6c-dce9-a1cf-feecb91f0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国施压下，以色列通讯部长表示当局将归还美联社扣押的设备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/israeli-officials-seize-ap-equipment-halt-gaza-live-broadcast-citing-al-jazeera-law/0000018f-9b4e-dce9-a1cf-ffce461c0000</link><description>以色列官员周二早些时候抵达以色列南部的美联社地点，没收了他们的设备，声称他们向半岛电视台提供加沙的图像，违反了该国新的外国广播公司法</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-21/ty-article/israeli-officials-seize-ap-equipment-halt-gaza-live-broadcast-citing-al-jazeera-law/0000018f-9b4e-dce9-a1cf-ffce461c0000</guid></item><item><title>校园抗议以色列的良性反犹太主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</link><description>示威者可以剥夺以色列人的生存权，因为在他们眼中，他们正在捍卫一个受到暴徒国家威胁的世界</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:32:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-virtuous-antisemitism-of-campus-protests-against-israel/0000018f-9aa0-d264-a1bf-deb7652f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>